 purpose only (...  otherwise see @{"'Distribution'" link "distribution" 0}).  You don't need to send money,
 gifts or anything else (but if you really want to ...).  But I would be glad if
            you send @{"me" link "contact" 0} an e-mail or a postcard if you like this set.


@endnode


@node requirements
@title "Requirements"

 This  set  of  transfer  animations  requires  one  of  the above mentioned WWW
 browsers (IBrowse, AWeb, Voyager).

 A  graphic  board is recommended but not required because of the five different
 colour depth (24 to 4 Bit).

 BTW: The difference between the 24 and 8 Bit version is hardly to be seen.

@endnode

@node install
@title "How to install??"

 If  you  are  a very, very experienced user, you can install this set "by hand"
 8-).  Otherwise wait for an installer script.

 No  ...  just kidding.  There is and there will be no installer script for this
 set of transfer animations.

 To  install  just grab the prefered anim and colour depth and the corresponding
 icon for your WWW browser.

 Now  rename  for  example  -  if  you want to use it with IBrowse - the anim to
 def_TransferAnimation  and the corresponding icon to def_TransferAnimation.info
 and  copy  both  files  into the IBrowse/Images directory (...  don't forget to
 backup  the  original  transfer animation ...  although there's no need anymore
 ;-)).

 ...    there  exist  a lot of variations and combinations of how to install the
 transfer animations ...  but I'm too lazy to decline all of them.

 It should not be that hard to install ...
 
@endnode

